@{
    ViewBag.HideSideBar = true;
}
@section scripts{
    <script>
        var isWin10 = function () {
            var e = navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();
            return e.indexOf("windows nt 10") >= 0;
        }

        $(function () {
            if (isWin10) {
                $("#a-win10-store").show();
            }
        });
    </script>
}

@section head{
    <style>
        .into-block-body-md {
            height: 130px;
        }

        .title-box {
            background-image: url(/images/img0.jpg);
            background-color: #000;
            padding: 70px 0;
        }

        @@media(max-width: 767px) {
            .into-block-body-md {
                height: inherit;
            }
        }
    </style>
}

<div class="title-box">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Apps for Windows 10</h1>
        <h3>Permanent free without Ads</h3>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="sec">
    <div class="container">
        <section id="featured">
            <h3>Tracing</h3>
            <hr />
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <img src="https://docs.edi.wang/images/tracing/ZH-1.png" class="img-fluid img-thumbnail" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        如果你喜欢画图但并不专业，没关系！只要选择你喜爱的图片，使用触控笔标描绘轮廓，就可以保存、分享或打印您的墨迹！拥有大量新特性及易用性改进，并支持Surface Dial等轮盘设备！
                    </blockquote>
                    <p>For Windows 10 v1803 and above</p>
                    <div>
                        <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/tracing/9nblggh6czcl" target="_blank" class="btn btn-success">Microsoft Store</a>
                        <a href="https://docs.edi.wang/tracing" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="sec sec-alter">
    <div class="container">
        <h3>Character Map UWP</h3>
        <hr />
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <blockquote class="blockquote">
                    Character Map, in UWP, it allows you to copy the selected character to XAML code and FontIcon, and export the character into high resolution PNG file
                </blockquote>
                <div>
                    <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/character-map-uwp/9wzdncrdxf41" class="btn btn-success">Microsoft Store</a>
                    <a href="http://ediwang.github.io/Character-Map-UWP/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/EdiWang/Character-Map-UWP/master/artifacts/main.png" class="img-fluid img-thumbnail" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

